eatmichael-jordannba\";s:10:\"feedburner\";a:1:{s:8:\"origlink\";s:64:\"http://technorati.com/sports/article/bulls-turn-up-heat-on-wade/\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:159:\"Bulls pressing for commitment from Flash, and ultimately, King James.<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/trarticles/~4/j5sOg462GW4\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";}i:2;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:37:\"Technology Addiction - A Subway Story\";s:6:\"author\";s:17:\"stefanialucchetti\";s:4:\"link\";s:59:\"http://feeds09.technorati.com/~r/trarticles/~3/akl_7jztJyw/\";s:4:\"guid\";s:77:\"http://technorati.com/technology/article/technology-addiction-a-subway-story/\";s:11:\"description\";s:188:\"Technology addiction is becoming an excuse for extreme rudeness.  A pregnant woman\'s subway story.<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/trarticles/~4/akl_7jztJyw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Sun, 04 Jul 2010 03:56:30 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:46:\"Technologyblackberrysubwaytechnology addiction\";s:10:\"feedburner\";a:1:{s:8:\"origlink\";s:77:\"http://technorati.com/technology/article/technology-addiction-a-subway-story/\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:188:\"Technology addiction is becoming an excuse for extreme rudeness.  A pregnant woman\'s subway story.<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/trarticles/~4/akl_7jztJyw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";}i:3;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:73:\"Google-ITA Deal Threatens Kayak, Orbitz, and Other Airfare Search Engines\";s:6:\"author\";s:9:\"kaleeltvp\";s:4:\"link\";s:59:\"http://feeds09.technorati.com/~r/trarticles/~3/RQ1P0ouFz2I/\";s:4:\"guid\";s:86:\"http://technorati.com/lifestyle/travel/article/google-ita-deal-threatens-kayak-orbitz/\";s:11:\"description\";s:231:\"Google\'s acquisition deal with ITA Software Inc will dominate all on line airfare searches, worrying on line agencies like Kayak and Expedia.<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/trarticles/~4/RQ1P0ouFz2I\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Sun, 04 Jul 2010 03:50:40 +0000\";s:8:\"